WEBVTT

00:04:59.565 --> 00:05:01.140
Sasa utauliza,

00:05:01.164 --> 00:05:03.822
"Kweli watu watataka shida hii yote?"

00:05:04.359 --> 00:05:07.718
Nadhani wanaweza kufanya kama wangepata
motisha,

00:05:07.742 --> 00:05:10.674
kama alama za uaminifu na
kurudishiwa fedha.

00:05:10.698 --> 00:05:12.908
Tuiite "pesa ya kijani."

00:05:13.419 --> 00:05:16.572
Kutakuwa na nafasi pana
mpya ya kupata pesa

00:05:16.596 --> 00:05:20.539
kutoka kwa hawa wateja wanaohitaji
kununua hizi bidhaa zinazorudishwa.

00:05:21.026 --> 00:05:24.341
Mfumo huu utatengeneza jambo la
kufurahisha kama ununuzi

00:05:24.365 --> 00:05:26.141
jaribu la kiroho

00:05:26.165 --> 00:05:28.810
ambalo linasaidia kuokoa sayari yetu.

00:05:28.834 --> 00:05:31.434
(Makofi)